    "It basically works by alerting cardholders in case of fraud attack detection.",
    "That can help to save the cardholders' money and increase the revenue yearly.",
    "The data comes from Vesta's real-world e-commerce transactions, which have a range of features that improve the efficiency of the alert system, and millions of people will benefit from them.",
